Interface SmartPhoneComponentsFactory

All Known Implementing Classes:
EUSmartPhoneComponentFactory, GlobalSmartPhoneComponentFactory, TurkeySmartPhoneComponentFactory
public interface SmartPhoneComponentsFactory
This interface represents a factory that the components of the phone will be produced.
